v>呬都珊那唎舍你<div class=jwxz>十四</div>多他阿去杀<div class=jwxz>二合</div>啰钵</span><span>那<div class=jwxz>十五</div>涅泥<div class=jwxz>上</div>舍<div class=jwxz>十六</div>输<div class=jwxz>引</div>地多<div class=jwxz>上</div>嚩底<div class=jwxz>十七</div>野他</span><span><div class=jwxz>引</div>①<br>多<div class=jwxz>十八</div>野他努句路<div class=jwxz>上</div>播么<div class=jwxz>十九</div>邬播莽涅</span><span>泥<div class=jwxz>上引</div>舍<div class=jwxz>二十</div>微庶<div class=jwxz>引</div>地多<div class=jwxz>二十一</div>怛多啰<div class=jwxz>二合</div>伽<div class=jwxz>引</div></span><span><div class=jwxz></div>丽<div class=jwxz>二十二</div>曩者羯答微阎<div class=jwxz>二合二十三</div>三钵啰<div class=jwxz>二合</div>娑</span></div>|<div class=jwk><span><div class=jwxz>引</div>娜遏他<div class=jwxz>二合</div>睹娑么<div class=jwxz>二十四</div>野他<div class=jwxz>引</div>怒句懒者</span><span>目佉<div class=jwxz>二十五</div>邬波僧贺啰喻舍<div class=jwxz>二十六</div>阿<div class=jwxz>引</div>舍耶</span><span>肆也<div class=jwxz>二合二十七</div>微庶<div class=jwxz>引</div>地耶<div class=jwxz>二十八</div>野他庶<div class=jwxz>引</div>地</span><span>底<div class=jwxz>二十九</div>罗去洒<div class=jwxz>二合</div>曩罗去洒<div class=jwxz>二合</div>你<div class=jwxz>三十</div>罗去洒</span><span><div class=jwxz>二合</div>曩嚩底<div class=jwxz>三十一</div>罗去洒<div class=jwxz>二合</div>囊微输驮你<div class=jwxz>三十二</div></div>@①：薛/女<br>|<div class=jwk><span><div class=jwxz></div>钵啰底吠驮遏他<div class=jwxz>三十三</div>珊那唎<div class=jwxz>二合</div>舍你<div class=jwxz>三十四</div></span><span><div class=jwxz></div>句舍啰冒他萨谜呵<div class=jwxz>三十五</div>钵啰<div class=jwxz>二合</div>微者曳<div class=jwxz>三十</div></span><span><div class=jwxz>六</div>娑么娑啰你<div class=jwxz>三十七</div>讫唎多<div class=jwxz>引</div>怒阿啰<div class=jwxz>二合</div>去</span><span>史<div class=jwxz>二合三十八</div>萨底也<div class=jwxz>二合</div>遏替<div class=jwxz>三十九</div>萨底也<div class=jwxz>二合</div>南</span><span><div class=jwxz>四十</div>素微输<div class=jwxz>引</div>地帝<div class=jwxz>四十一</div></span></div>|<div class=jwk><span>佛言无边庄严此是能摄净信者句及授与</span><span>句由是当能授与说此法师善品及义善男</span><span>子我今复说摧伏不信者句即说咒曰</span><span>去洒<div class=jwxz>二合</div>迷<div